&lt;li style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: 400;&quot;&gt;Partners with HR leadership on recruitment initiatives and drives the creation and delivery of retention efforts, and monitors for success.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
